  header.marquees.fill(style="background-image: url('https://static.wixstatic.com/media/2df143_cfc976f207534ff79f3b4828e2e97363~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_932,h_665,al_t,q_85/2df143_cfc976f207534ff79f3b4828e2e97363~mv2.jpg'); height:100vh; background-size:cover; ")
    .container-fluid.text-center
      h1.title-text HELPING PEOPLE WHO NEED TO KNOW
      h3.title-subText RedRibbon.US was created to provide the Dallas community impacted by HIV/AIDS with a centralized repository of up-to-date, accurate information regarding local services.

  .container-fluid.about-container
    .row
      .col-md-12.text-center
        div.box-shadow
          h1 ABOUT US
          h5 Bringing the Community Together... for YOU
          br
          p We are creating a centralized and update-to-date platform that allows those impacted by HIV (whether they are the patient, a parent, sibling or friend) an easily navigable site to find resources that will save their lives. <br> We are excited to have been selected as the focus project for the inaugural #FirstHack event and look forward to launching our full site in Q4 2016. <br> Our site will be driven by the community, and while we are starting in the North Texas area, we see potential to rapidly begin to support communities nation-wide.

  .container-fluid
    .row.cta-row1
      .col-md-6.boxes.box1
        div.overlay
        div.box-text
          h1 Community Building
        div.hover-text
          p Education and paticipation are the key to survival for those impacted by HIV - we will build a community that will support its members.

      .col-md-6.boxes.box2
        div.overlay
        div.box-text
          div.box-text
            h1 Support Services
          div.hover-text
            p People often need a helping hand - but to get that help they need to know who to call and what they will need.  We will provide up-to-date information on services available (food, shelter, counselling, healthcare, etc.) including detailed service descriptions, and comprehensive requirements for services - all available in a centralized location.

    .row.cta-row2
      .col-md-6.boxes.box3
        div.overlay
        div.box-text
          h1 Building a Community
        div.hover-text
          p Our goal is not to build a static site, but rather an online community where members can contribute ideas and information, as well as asking questions, all in a safe environment.

      .col-md-6.boxes.box4
        div.overlay
        div.box-text
          h1 Support
        div.hover-text
          p Finding support is critical - we will provide it in an anonymous, secure environment that places the need of our members for privacy above all else

